            <div class="_1YzQk _3bFZi">
             <h3 class="_2XVos _1On_l" data-pb-type="hl" data-testid="article-headline">
              <a data-testid="article-link" href="https://www.watoday.com.au/please-explain" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">
               Please Explain podcast
              </a>
             </h3>
             <p class="_3XEsE" data-pb-type="ab">
              Expert daily insight into the stories that drive the nation.
             </p>
            </div>
           </div>
          </div>
          <div class="MqudN">

               <source data-pb-im-config='{"aspectRatio":1,"type":"square1x1","width":72}' media="(min-width: 768px)" srcset="https://static.ffx.io/images/$zoom_0.39211618257261416%2C$multiply_0.1905%2C$ratio_1%2C$width_378%2C$x_67%2C$y_0/t_crop_custom/q_86%2Cf_auto/b1a6b767c85f6421e37ce97a78497c524c024068, https://static.ffx.io/images/$zoom_0.39211618257261416%2C$multiply_0.381%2C$ratio_1%2C$width_378%2C$x_67%2C$y_0/t_crop_custom/q_62%2Cf_auto/b1a6b767c85f6421e37ce97a78497c524c024068 2x"/>
               <img alt="The vineyard of Swinney Wines in the Great Southern wine region of Frankland River." class="_1MQMh" src="https://static.ffx.io/images/$zoom_0.39211618257261416%2C$multiply_0.1905%2C$ratio_1%2C$width_378%2C$x_67%2C$y_0/t_crop_custom/q_86%2Cf_auto/b1a6b767c85f6421e37ce97a78497c524c024068" srcset="https://static.ffx.io/images/$zoom_0.39211618257261416%2C$multiply_0.1905%2C$ratio_1%2C$width_378%2C$x_67%2C$y_0/t_crop_custom/q_86%2Cf_auto/b1a6b767c85f6421e37ce97a78497c524c024068, https://static.ffx.io/images/$zoom_0.39211618257261416%2C$multiply_0.381%2C$ratio_1%2C$width_378%2C$x_67%2C$y_0/t_crop_custom/q_62%2Cf_auto/b1a6b767c85f6421e37ce97a78497c524c024068 2x"/>
              </picture>
             </div>
            </a>
           </figure>
           <p class="_3XEsE" data-pb-type="ab">
            Everything has an origin story, and good wine starts in the vineyard. As wineries move to minimalist methods, the end product has never been more reflective of the origin.
           </p>
          </div>
         </div>
        </div>
        <div class="_1QYal">
         <div class="_15r1L _1Wer5 _3TEmE _3FJrM _38s9o _2ubQC" data-an-position="4" data-pb-type="st" data-testid="story-tile">
          <div class="_1YzQk">
           <div class="_3XK8N">
            <h5 class="_1XJ15" data-pb-type="tg">
             <a href="/topic/wa-police-jkq">
              Police
             </a>
            </h5>
           </div>

              </picture>
             </div>
            </a>
           </figure>
           <p class="_3XEsE" data-pb-type="ab">
            Police are targeting criminal networks made up of people and companies linked to the cattle business, including musterers, livestock trucking companies, truck drivers, stock agents, abattoirs and feed lots.
           </p>
          </div>
         </div>

           <h3 class="_2XVos" data-pb-type="hl" data-testid="article-headline">
            <a data-testid="article-link" href="/sport/afl/suns-star-matt-rowell-injured-as-west-coast-wins-season-opening-thriller-at-optus-stadium-20210321-p57cpr.html">

            </a>

          <div class="_1YzQk _24ZSP">
           <div class="_3XK8N">
            <h5 class="_2EuJH" data-pb-type="lb">
             Analysis
            </h5>
            <h5 class="_1XJ15" data-pb-type="tg">
             <a href="/topic/afl-2021-1nls">

           <h3 class="_2XVos" data-pb-type="hl" data-testid="article-headline">
            <a data-testid="article-link" href="/sport/afl/four-points-why-this-was-the-opening-round-we-and-the-afl-needed-20210321-p57clr.html">
             Why this was the opening round we and the AFL needed
            </a>
           </h3>
           <p class="_3XEsE" data-pb-type="ab">
            The first round offered an excellent suite of matches and a feeling that the game was back to where it had been when at its best.
           </p>
